<title>UK: GSI sets warrants on Baloise.</title>
<headline>GSI sets warrants on Baloise.</headline>
<dateline>LONDON 1997-04-25</dateline>
<text>
<p>Goldman Sachs International has issued three million American-style call warrants, on Baloise registered shares, lead manager Goldman Sachs &amp; Co. Bank said.</p>
<p>One share is controlled by 50 warrants.</p>
<p> STRIKE PRICE    3200 CHF		  PREMIUM	13.7 PCT</p>
<p> ISSUE PRICE     4.90 CHF		  GEARING	12.37 X</p>
<p> EXERCISE PERIOD 13.MAY.97-17.JUL.98   PAYDATE	12.MAY.97</p>
<p> LISTING	   SWISS EXCHANGE	  MIN EXER LOT 500</p>
<p> SPOT REFERENCE  3030 CHF</p>
<p> NOTES</p>
<p>-- Reuter London Newsroom +44 171 542 7658</p>
